<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 14:04:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>印第安纳波利斯酒吧致命枪击案嫌疑人已被拘留，造成 1 人死亡、5 人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/suspect-in-custody-in-deadly-bar-shooting-in-indianapolis-that-killed-1-injured-5/articleshow/108563481.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108563481.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;警方称，周六清晨印第安纳波利斯一家酒吧发生枪击事件，造成 1 人死亡、5 人受伤，一名名叫尼古拉斯·富尔克 (Nicholas Fulk) 的嫌疑人被捕。据当局称，25 岁​​的富尔克在 Broad Ripple Avenue 的 Landsharks 枪击事件发生几小时后，因初步指控谋杀而被捕。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 10:49:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/suspect-in-custody-in-deadly-bar-shooting-in-indianapolis-that-killed-1-injured-5/articleshow/108563481.cms</guid></item><item><title>冰岛自12月以来第四次喷发后熔岩流动缓慢</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/iceland-lava-flows-slow-after-fourth-eruption-since-december/articleshow/108563462.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108563462.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 10:48:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/iceland-lava-flows-slow-after-fourth-eruption-since-december/articleshow/108563462.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯加强海军火力应对乌克兰无人机袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-boosts-navy-firepower-to-counter-ukrainian-drone-attacks/articleshow/108562974.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108562974.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯加强海军力量，应对乌克兰在黑海的无人机袭击。随着双方为争夺优势而进行战略演习，冲突不断升级。国防部长谢尔盖·绍伊古表示：“必须每天对人员进行培训。培训如何击退空中和无人艇的袭击。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 10:52:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-boosts-navy-firepower-to-counter-ukrainian-drone-attacks/articleshow/108562974.cms</guid></item><item><title>华盛顿特区夜间发生枪击事件，造成 2 人死亡、5 人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/overnight-shooting-in-washington-dc-kills-2-wounds-5/articleshow/108562790.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108562790.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 10:16:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/overnight-shooting-in-washington-dc-kills-2-wounds-5/articleshow/108562790.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国启动第四级紧急救援，救援人员在中国四川扑灭山火</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-activates-level-iv-emergency-as-rescuers-battle-wildfires-in-chinas-sichuan/articleshow/108561864.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108561864.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 09:01:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-activates-level-iv-emergency-as-rescuers-battle-wildfires-in-chinas-sichuan/articleshow/108561864.cms</guid></item><item><title>非洲中国工人数量降至最低水平</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/number-of-chinese-workers-across-africa-drops-to-lowest-level/articleshow/108562118.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108562118.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 09:22:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/number-of-chinese-workers-across-africa-drops-to-lowest-level/articleshow/108562118.cms</guid></item><item><title>“固定比赛”：伊姆兰·汗要求对“窃取人民授权”的巴基斯坦官员提起叛国罪诉讼</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/fixed-match-imran-khan-demands-high-treason-proceedings-against-pak-officials-who-stole-peoples-mandate/articleshow/108562017.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108562017.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊姆兰·汗 (Imran Khan) 呼吁对巴基斯坦选举涉嫌操纵、质疑法院命令和选举程序、腐败案件持续发酵以及对经济形势的批评等指控提起叛国罪诉讼。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 09:14:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/fixed-match-imran-khan-demands-high-treason-proceedings-against-pak-officials-who-stole-peoples-mandate/articleshow/108562017.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯指责乌克兰进行“恐怖活动”扰乱总统选举</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-accuses-ukraine-of-terrorist-activities-to-disrupt-presidential-election/articleshow/108560368.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108560368.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯指责乌克兰从事“恐怖活动”以扰乱其总统选举，乌克兰战争给乌克兰持续的选举蒙上阴影。前总统德米特里·梅德韦杰夫谴责抗议者是破坏投票站的“叛徒”。随着事件升级，紧张局势加剧，有人警告称将造成严重后果，并支持反对克里姆林宫的武装团体。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 07:21:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-accuses-ukraine-of-terrorist-activities-to-disrupt-presidential-election/articleshow/108560368.cms</guid></item><item><title>布林肯抵达韩国出席民主峰会</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/blinken-arrives-in-south-korea-to-attend-democracy-summit/articleshow/108562127.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108562127.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周日抵达韩国，这是其短暂亚洲之行的第一站，菲律宾也包括在内，华盛顿正在采取行动加强与两个主要地区盟友的关系。布林肯周日下午在周一举行的第三次民主峰会之前抵达，这是美国总统乔·拜登的倡议，首尔本周将主办该峰会。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 09:23:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/blinken-arrives-in-south-korea-to-attend-democracy-summit/articleshow/108562127.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京准备在有限的反对下再统治俄罗斯六年</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-poised-to-rule-russia-for-another-six-years-amid-limited-opposition/articleshow/108560110.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108560110.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统普京在受控的选举环境中以极少的反对和没有公开批评的方式获得了另一个六年的任期。对手纳瓦尔尼的缺席导致批评者入狱或流放。尽管面临一些小挑战，普京仍面临着乌克兰无人机袭击等持续存在的问题。经济坚韧，国防工业支撑。反对派呼吁通过投票进行抗议。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 07:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-poised-to-rule-russia-for-another-six-years-amid-limited-opposition/articleshow/108560110.cms</guid></item><item><title>“一位候选人太老了，精神上不适合……”：拜登在华盛顿新闻晚宴上嘲讽特朗普</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-roasts-trump-at-washington-press-dinner/articleshow/108559735.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108559735.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 81 岁的美国总统乔·拜登在烤架俱乐部幽默地表达了人们对他与 77 岁的特朗普相比年龄的担忧。他批评共和党人优先考虑他儿子的商业调查，主张乌克兰对俄罗斯提供军事援助，并抨击特朗普的流行病应对措施。拜登强调了民主的重要性，并赞扬了活动中以幽默和友情而闻名的记者。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 06:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-roasts-trump-at-washington-press-dinner/articleshow/108559735.cms</guid></item><item><title>南苏丹关闭所有学校，为应对极端热浪做准备</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-sudan-shutters-all-schools-as-it-prepares-for-an-extreme-heat-wave/articleshow/108561963.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108561963.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于酷热，南苏丹学校关闭两周，建议家长让孩子呆在室内，以避免 45 摄氏度的高温。各部委表示，他们“将继续监测情况，并相应地通知公众。”居住在首都的居民彼得·加朗表示，“学校应该连接到电网”，以便安装空调。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 09:12:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-sudan-shutters-all-schools-as-it-prepares-for-an-extreme-heat-wave/articleshow/108561963.cms</guid></item><item><title>住宿危机：亚利桑那州允许工人睡在车里</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/accommodation-crisis-arizona-city-to-allow-workers-to-sleep-in-their-cars/articleshow/108560874.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108560874.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;塞多纳市议会批准了“安全公园”倡议，允许无家可归的工人在高昂的住房成本下睡在车里。该计划提供配有设施的指定地点，由亚利桑那州住房部资助。批评者对污染和非法活动表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 08:52:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/accommodation-crisis-arizona-city-to-allow-workers-to-sleep-in-their-cars/articleshow/108560874.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国儿童面临暴力和自残内容的风险：报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-children-exposed-to-risks-of-violent-and-self-harm-content-report/articleshow/108558907.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108558907.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国的儿童，甚至是小学年龄的儿童，都会在网上接触暴力和自残内容，这给政府和科技巨头带来了挑战。最近的研究强调了未成年人在社交媒体和消息平台上遇到有害内容的情况。法规旨在保护儿童，但执行面临障碍。科技公司迫切需要优先考虑儿童安全。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 07:43:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-children-exposed-to-risks-of-violent-and-self-harm-content-report/articleshow/108558907.cms</guid></item><item><title>“只有少数人知道……”：凯特·米德尔顿的缺席引起了员工的担忧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/only-few-people-know-kate-middletons-absence-raises-concern-among-staff/articleshow/108559982.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108559982.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;接近白金汉宫的消息人士透露，米德尔顿的一些主要助手甚至在手术向公众宣布之前都不知道这一消息，这引起了他们的惊讶和担忧。 《美国周刊》报道称，“凯特的一些高级工作人员一直未能见到她或与她交谈，他们甚至在手术宣布之前才知道这件事，所以这让他们措手不及，”《美国周刊》援引报道称来源。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 06:57:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/only-few-people-know-kate-middletons-absence-raises-concern-among-staff/articleshow/108559982.cms</guid></item><item><title>冰岛火山再次喷发熔岩，这是自 2023 年 12 月以来的第四次喷发</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/iceland-volcano-shoots-lava-into-air-as-it-erupts-again-4th-time-since-december-2023/articleshow/108557592.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108557592.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;冰岛的一座火山自十二月以来第四次喷发，呈现出熔岩喷泉和流动的熔岩。雷克雅未克附近2.9公里长的裂缝喷发引发紧急状态，但凯夫拉维克机场仍在运营。冰岛拥有 30 座活火山，尽管人们对火山的担忧持续存在，但其火山性质仍然吸引着火山游客。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 06:22:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/iceland-volcano-shoots-lava-into-air-as-it-erupts-again-4th-time-since-december-2023/articleshow/108557592.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰在俄罗斯总统选举最后一天发动大范围无人机袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-launches-far-ranging-drone-attacks-on-final-day-of-russias-presidential-vote/articleshow/108559198.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108559198.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 06:10:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-launches-far-ranging-drone-attacks-on-final-day-of-russias-presidential-vote/articleshow/108559198.cms</guid></item><item><title>“整个国家的大屠杀”：特朗普警告如果他输掉总统选举</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/bloodbath-for-whole-country-trump-warns-if-he-loses-us-presidential-elections/articleshow/108556649.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108556649.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;特朗普周六宣布，11 月的总统选举将是美国历史上“最重要的日期”，并警告称，如果他没有获胜，将“引发一场大屠杀”。他说：“现在，如果我没有当选，这将是整个国家的一场大屠杀，这只是最不重要的，这将是整个国家的一场大屠杀。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 03:11:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/bloodbath-for-whole-country-trump-warns-if-he-loses-us-presidential-elections/articleshow/108556649.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼日尔政府断绝与美国的军事合作</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/niger-breaks-off-military-cooperation-with-us-govt/articleshow/108556204.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108556204.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尼日尔政府周六宣布，“立即”终止与美国的军事合作协议。尼日尔军方过去曾与美国密切合作。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 02:06:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/niger-breaks-off-military-cooperation-with-us-govt/articleshow/108556204.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着投票巩固普京的控制，乌克兰袭击了俄罗斯</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukrainian-strikes-rock-russia-as-vote-cements-putins-grip/articleshow/108554630.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108554630.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周六，在弗拉基米尔·普京总统领导下的总统选举期间，乌克兰的空袭造成两人死亡，并导致俄罗斯一处石油设施起火。由于乌克兰袭击事件增多以及亲乌克兰团体渗透到俄罗斯境内，投票进程受到干扰。新的轰炸促使当局关闭了与乌克兰接壤的别尔哥罗德地区的学校和购物中心。</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 23:09:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukrainian-strikes-rock-russia-as-vote-cements-putins-grip/articleshow/108554630.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>